{
  "stem": "14212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we remained in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At that time, a Jewish Polkovnik, a high military official, who used to be the connector between the Soviet Union and the Polish army, which was created in the Soviet Union due to an agreement with the-- the Polish general.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And came over and told us, look-- and he said it in Jewish-- maybe it's better for you that they are going to have a possibility of not coming back.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if you'll stay here, believe me, the Germans will not come here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in Kermine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kermine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remained in Kermine there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As an invalid, I joined the [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Altel, ?] a group of-- [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Altel ?] is a group of entertainment-- like--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not entertainment, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Enterprises.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Enterprises, excuse me-- tailors, shoemakers, restaurant, barbers, carpenters--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This type-- services.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I joined them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I worked myself up to the position of the leader-- the technical leader of the [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Altel. ?] And I worked until one day, I was approached in a way that I couldn't resist to go become the administrator of the Polish Children's Home.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After the departure of the Poles from-- from the Soviet Union, there were still-- they had Polish children, mostly Jewish whose parents perished-- they died of all kind of diseases which were there at that time-- and Polish children, Ukrainian children, which belonged to Poland before.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Soviet Union created a number of these Polish children's homes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from that day, we had a supervisor, which was a Jew, a communist from Leningrad, by the name of Mr.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Berizanski.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I worked as administrator.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had a lady from Krakow by the name of Miss Singer.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
